name: fineoakstructure
text:
So what's up with this strip (in Assetbar terms)?

- Only 9 comments (as of 10/16/08) so far, none older than a month.

- only 2834 views, compared to 88085 on the strip before and 36412 on the strip after. They aren't reruns, but similar strips have a lot more views than ~3000.

- Plus, I don't know about anyone else, but all of a sudden this strip (and the latest strip at the time, which I hadn't looked at yet) showed up in my "You haven't seen these most commented" lists, which I had long ago cycled all the way through and had defaulted back to the top strips.

Was this strip somehow missing from Assetbar until recently, or did it suddenly reveal itself to me? I started to think it might have to do with some "milestone" I hit recently (1000 comments or chubbies or something...), but it doesn't look like those necessarily match with all the other commenters here.

Odd.

text: The people still love life and other people. Even in the guts of Bangkok (the word "guts" chosen for obvious reasons of anyone that's been there).
